PiMAME Installer

http://pimame.org

For the Raspberry Pi

sudo apt-get install git
git clone https://github.com/ssilverm/pimame_installer
cd pimame_installer
./pimame.py

Install will fully install PiMAME, including Web Frontend, FTP server, etc
Update will update PiMAME (will not overwrite custom config files)
Remove will totally remove PiMAME :(